705
00:38:43.868 --> 00:38:45.062
No, I'm just a botanist.

706
00:38:45.136 --> 00:38:47.468
Look, kids, after all,
you know, this is only a zipper.


707
00:38:47.539 --> 00:38:49.769
- Come on, Gurky.
- Well, I can try.


708
00:38:49.841 --> 00:38:52.105
You know, I had this happen one night
in the middle of my act.


709
00:38:52.177 --> 00:38:55.010
I couldn't get a thing off,
was I embarrassed.


710
00:38:55.080 --> 00:38:56.479
How's chances for a cup of coffee?

711
00:38:56.548 --> 00:38:59.540
- No breakfast after 9:00.
- You see, it's a rule.


712
00:38:59.618 --> 00:39:02.712
Just like my Aunt Beulah that
