713
00:39:02.787 --> 00:39:03.776
- There.
- Oh, swell.


714
00:39:03.855 --> 00:39:05.618
Now where is this little clambake
of Professor Potts'?


715
00:39:05.690 --> 00:39:09.091
- In the dining room, just across the hall.
- In the dining room. See you later, kids.


716
00:39:13.965 --> 00:39:17.128
